  "bio_raw": "He is highly motivated and technically adept Computer Science and IT professional with a strong academic foundation and hands-on experience in research, cloud computing, and software development. He is adept at designing and deploying cloud-based solutions, working with DevOps tools, and implementing CI/CD pipelines. He is a published researcher with multiple contributions in networking, cloud computing, IoT, ML and cybersecurity. He possesses a proven ability to lead teams, manage projects, and contribute to academic conferences. He is well experienced in programming with Python, C++, and Java, as well as frameworks like Django and Node.js. He has successfully managed large-scale projects, including enterprise web applications and fraud detection systems. He is well passionate about leveraging technology to drive innovation and efficiency in both academic and professional settings. Moreover, he holds a master’s in information technology from Deakin University and a bachelor’s in computer science from BRAC University. He is well recognized for leadership, problem-solving skills, and a commitment to continuous learning.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Networking, Cloud Computing, IoT, Machine Learning, Neural Networks, Geographic Information System (GIS)"
  ],
  "education": [
    {
