  ],
  "publications_raw": [
    "Conference Proceedings\nM. K. Hossain\n, M. Rahman, A. Hossain, S. Y. Rahman and M. M. Islam,” Active & Idle Virtual Machine Migration Algorithm- a new Ant Colony Optimization approach to consolidate Virtual Machines and ensure Green Cloud Computing,” 2020 Emerging Technology in Computing, Communication and Electronics (ETCCE), Bangladesh, 2020, pp. 1-6.\nM. K. Hossain\n, T. Promi and P. Paul,” Credit card fraudulence detection using Salient Feature Extraction Technique with Adaptive Synthetic Oversampling Models,” 2021 24\nth\nInternational Conference on Computer and Information Technology (ICCIT), Dhaka, Bangladesh, 2021, pp. 1-6.\nM. K. Hossain\n,” Smart & Scalable Lighting System Using Motion Sensors, Light Dependent Resistors and ESP8266 Controller Board,” 2024 IEEE International Conference on Advanced Systems and Emergent Technologies (ICASET), Hammamet, Tunisia, 2024, pp. 1-6.\nM. K. Hossain\n,” Migration of Idle Machines via Parking Server – a new sophisticated Ant Colony Optimization algorithm to address Green Cloud Computing,” 2024 4th International Conference on Intelligent Technologies (CONIT), Bangalore, India, 2024, pp. 1-5.\nM. K. Hossain\n,” A Neural Network Learning Approach Using ConvNet Models to Consolidate Corneal Ulcer Detection in Opthalmology,” 2024 IEEE International Conference on Artificial Intelligence in Engineering and Technology (IICAIET), Kota Kinabalu, Malaysia, 2024, pp. 36-41.\nCredit Card Fraud Detection using Big Data and Deep Learning Algorithms (Published in BRAC University ICBM 2021)\nS. M. Dipto, M. Islam, S. M. A. A. Mamun,\nM. K. Hossain\n, A. M. Esfar-E-Alam and M. A. Alam, \"An Interpretable Transformer-Based Approach to Classify Malaria from Blood Cell Images,\"\n2024 International Conference on Sustainable Technology and Engineering (i-COSTE)\n, Perth, Australia, 2024, pp. 1-6, doi: 10.1109/i-COSTE63786.2024.11024978\nA. H. Raiyan, J. T. Eara, S. K. Oishi and\nM. K. Hossain\n, \"Deep Feature Fusion with Ensemble Learning for Robust & Scalable Detection of DDoS, Zero-Day & Malware Attacks,\"\n2026 IEEE 2nd International Conference on Quantum Photonics, Artificial Intelligence & Networking (QPAIN)\n, Chittagong, Bangladesh, 2026, pp. 1-6, doi: 10.1109/QPAIN69676.2026.11546051.\nA. H. Raiyan, J. T. Eara, S. K. Oishi and\nM. K. Hossain\n, \"Boosting Diagnostic Accuracy for Gastric Cancer Detection Using Super Resolution Driven Resnet50, VGG19 & DenseNet121,\"\n2025 28th International Conference on Computer and Information Technology (ICCIT)\n, Cox's Bazar, Bangladesh, 2025, pp. 5010-5015, doi: 10.1109/ICCIT68739.2025.11491694.",
